Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好...好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同志们 和寒冷战斗到底啊 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个混蛋说今年是暖冬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿三倍衣服过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草间老师太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是雪啊 雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再吹风了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高...高见女子高中的同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们应该是坐前一列特快来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 苍荣的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍荣高中的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻装上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全副武装
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么天寒地冻的你们这是干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4天3夜的冬季合宿 in 长白鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小看冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 所以画好正确的装备寄给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:55.36,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山猫座炭：不穿得暖暖的是不行的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是不是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下半身都是光光的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是毛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们首先要面对的就是寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那细微的缝隙里一点一点传来的寒气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有克服了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能在冷天里进行活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是星见妹妹和小矢 准备得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学和江户川同学需要再套一层
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样也是好好准备了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧身牛仔裤穿了和没穿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的冬天装备是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化纤织料这类能够吸汗速干的衣料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中间的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绒布或是毛衣这类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以留住空气的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不透风的材料最好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作裤之类的 能很好的留住体温
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有帽子发热片等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再适当地加上各种各样的附加装备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好带了些能加的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也把短衬裤穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也带了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是以为白天会热而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了 其他事情再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次请多多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客气 毕竟要4天3夜在同吃同住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜一下子就歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 大美女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也一起来打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 你不是新部长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有在高天联见过了的么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地打招呼...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐们也很紧张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就心跳如小鹿一般...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生相片 让我照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气转晴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里天气很多变的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小杉野市的今年还没开始下雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没见到这么厚的雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 美星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都去过那么多地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看到这种情景还那么兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸还在的时候虽然经常带我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在了以后就不怎么出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要说对不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么 恋爱关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一般学校里不是到处都是情侣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的世界观有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们办事疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连合宿的地方都没定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是 能一起来我们很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍荣的同学们是第一次来冬季合宿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为天文部是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过冬季的星座都已经很熟悉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户座和昴星团
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季大三角和冬季大六角形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然见过但也只是在城市里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 绝对会让你们更感动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 星见妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得猎户座是美男子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是大胡子猎人大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想要美男子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样打扮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里反而应该是大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你萌胡子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文台圆顶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到室内呼出的气还是白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖气供应有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都这样的 过会儿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食堂在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿我们要自己做饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 先去看看自己的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把行李给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人拿得动的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生宿舍在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面装了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻 秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等会见 小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有暖贴也拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双脚已经没感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今为止都没这样玩过雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好换上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 女高中生之间居然有那么多的身体接触
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户川？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我可要往死里的照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三波同学 秋菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是来帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设营啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样的话会被雪冻伤的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这次要做什么观测？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往年都是年初的时候来合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测四分仪座流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年因为月光的原因只好改了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以主要是观察和摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们来说是最后一次合宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能尽兴就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不放晴的话也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来合宿就把这个因素考虑进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自己选的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直喊好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先找些能一起穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧身裤和作睡衣的运动裤都穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿不上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来只是想要在雪景里穿得可爱点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的时候在车上看到了好像是便利店的店铺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有保暖内衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 不要让手脚发冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二 要随身携带好自己的手电筒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三 出门前要告诉别人自己去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好有这些亲和力高的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来播报各地天气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上空有强冷空气 受其影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在长白鹤地区可能突降大雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请留意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长白鹤地区？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店不哪里都是24小时营业的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且美星说看到她到外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天都黑了 为什么她要一个人出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没听我们说的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 她那时就不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定没听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们修暖气的时候竟然发生这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种大雪里 一个不习惯风雪天气的孩子独自在外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先在旅馆里再找一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她确实带够了备用的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你看到她时的情形详细地...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白茫茫一片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要挖个洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到大家那里就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 要镇定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要顺着自己的脚印就能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的脚印...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西南北都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能走远了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本看不清前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古今中外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 到我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么窗子开着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是睡觉的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说啊 我白天可是很努力的干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那一望无际的雪铲啊铲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了设营的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能让我玩一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学她不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星大概也追出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经联系消防队了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的暴风雪下不知什么时候能来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那两人能找到一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在播放各地的天气情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长白鹤地区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要镇静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有可能是为了摄影取景到后面的森林去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把范围定在公交站的那个方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去找丢了的东西的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回到了镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常还是会发生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是摄影点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再前面就是雪地和森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视野也不好 很容易迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是傻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冻成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家多么担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方离别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还那么年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想要多打扮自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有亲吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有告白过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生才刚刚开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使不出力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是天谴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 电钻头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来叫声「电钻头」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么电钻头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电钻头 电钻头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那是天生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这下 恐怕真的糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得那么漂亮的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:15:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小熊炭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小熊炭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点紧张感都没有的白痴卡通是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HOT！ 小熊暖贴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 我才没有带这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大龄...美星学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你一个人出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不见你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想你是不是迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身是什么装备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 运动服？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回到大家那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷进去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 完全找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在车站的话 恐怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我们一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这样太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝对不会胡来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬小姬 美星学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了 小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是先把手电筒给我了 会什么后果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后还是不知道方向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 天晴了就会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意！ 现在还在下大雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正好有个能避雪的洞 太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35\fad(500,500)\c&H4E3B93&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\blur4}把美星拖出来留下的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈你来干嘛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很感谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我能理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我以前也一个人在下大雪时跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后挨骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为穿过大雪就能看到星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然非常冷 心里也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风雪后的星空果然好美丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 偷跑出来也要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会很伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如在云端般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么轻快...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在高处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人在下面嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊那里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你关心我 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后沦落到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说学姐是云的话 我就是雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越积越厚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道现在不是说这些的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是学姐 请再正视我一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果学姐不把我当作对手的话 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会认输的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于大八木同学的感情我也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风停了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕宿五 参宿七 五车二 北河三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参宿四 南河三 天狼星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星太多了 都连不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光...箭？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果迷失了方向 要注意到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 乱来也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了有事尽管跟我们说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服的话想要多少都借你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太担心 小夜都憔悴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们平安无事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气也好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖炉弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 终于能暖暖身子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始做准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏要开场了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点神志不清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来比谁在室外观星的持续时间更长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能找到更好的观星地点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手 对手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟以为我说的是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.87,0:23:47.77,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫追星社 最终回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:49.56,Preview,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星空环
